title: Crimes That Shook Britain - Season 5
description:
Crimes That Shook Britain - Season 5

Investigate some of Britain's most horrendous murdersthrough the eyes of the people at the core of the crime. With reconstructions, key interviews and archive material, you can piece together the last moments of the victim's life and how the fall-out from the crime led to significant changes in British law. This series uncovers the real stories behind six of the largest crimes to hit the UK.
